OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Fri 8 May to Sun 17 May
OL,6,FThere is a lot of uncertainty in the
OL,7,Fevolution through this period, more so
OL,8,Fthan normal, but overall it would
OL,9,Fappear that a rather unsettled theme
OL,10,Fis most likely. Most places are
OL,11,Ftherefore likely to see some rain or
OL,12,Fshowers at times, but also some drier,
OL,13,Fbrighter weather. The emphasis on
OL,14,Fwetter conditions may be more towards
OL,15,Fthe south at first, with low pressure
OL,16,Fperhaps more likely towards the south
OL,17,Fof the UK, before shifting further
OL,18,Fnorth later in the period as low
OL,19,Fpressure becomes more likely to set up
OL,20,Fto the north of the UK. Temperatures
OL,21,Fare likely to be near normal in the
OL,22,Fsouth throughout but on the cool side
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,23,Fin the north at first before
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
OL,24,Frecovering to around normal later.
FL,164,160,301,260,100,100
PN,16303
SC,0003
CT,20,T
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F163A1777813862
OL,1,Wj5hw1~{4k7juhw1{$             G3/3
OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sun 17 May to Sun 31 May
OL,6,FLow pressure systems are likely to
OL,7,Fdominate across the UK at the start of
OL,8,Fthis period. This means showers or
OL,9,Flonger spells of rain are likely at
OL,10,Ftimes, heavy in places, with the
OL,11,Fwettest conditions probably towards
OL,12,Fthe northwest. There will, however,
OL,13,Fprobably be some dry and warm
OL,14,Finterludes, these more likely towards
OL,15,Fthe south, although temperatures are
OL,16,Flikely to be close to normal overall.
OL,17,FLater in the month, more settled and
OL,18,Fdrier conditions may begin to develop,
OL,19,Fwith temperatures perhaps rising above
OL,20,Fnormal.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
FL,164,160,301,260,100,100
